	"2e3c9e69-1f9e-4647-8d13-4e88094d2790":  {
		"0":  {
			"value": "The 7th Plane is a highly customized game, featuring a completely original world and mythos. The primary foci of the game are PvE and\u00a0character building, with a heavy emphasis on crafting, but there are\u00a0also options for PvP and RP. Some of the game\u2019s more\u00a0prominent features include: advanced NPC AI, physics based game mechanics, player configurable waypoints with path-finding algorithms, a creature dissection system, and over 100 different crafting resources.<br \/><br \/>[play=7thplane.net:8888]"
		}
	},
