			"value": "[play=akanbar.com:23]<br \/><br \/>Akanbar is a role playing game that takes place in a land of medieval fantasy where dragons, ogres and magic exist. With three realms to live in, the Sun realm, the Shadow realm and the Demonic realm, you can play whatever role you wish, be it a stealthy Assassin or a dragon-riding Storm Warden. Each realm hosts a city and, within that city, many guilds to choose from. Should hunting or player-killing not attract you, there are countless other activities to do, ranging from completing quests to creating items."
