	"2e3c9e69-1f9e-4647-8d13-4e88094d2790": {
		"0": {
			"value": "[play=ansalon.net:8679]<br \/><br \/>Welcome to Ansalon, a Dragonlance MUD (Multi User Dungeon, Text Based Game) where a player can become an imaginary character in the DragonLance world, and interact with other players who are also playing at the same time. Your character can be a Silvanesti Elf, a Neidar Dwarf, a Human, a Minotaur, a fun-loving Kender, or any of a multitude of races. <br \/><br \/>Ansalon is one of the longest-running MUDs left in existence (est. 1996). It is a stable, well-developed world, with custom code and custom areas to explore. Even over a decade later, we\u2019re making upgrades and changes on a weekly basis!"
		}
