			"value": "<p>We offer heart-pounding PK, deep role play and diverse interaction opportunities in a well-established classic fantasy MUD that is based on D&amp;D rules.\u00a0 We are also 100% free.<\/p>\r\n<p>Carrion Fields has 16 well-defined and balanced classes, multiple races, and an enormous, original world.\u00a0 Additionally we have a broad pantheon of immortal religions, constant game development and a friendly community.<br \/><br \/>If you enjoy a challenging and undiluted gaming experience full of hidden twists, RP immersion and fast paced combat, we are the game for you.<br \/><br \/><br \/>[play=208.117.43.240:4449]<\/p>"
		}
