			"value": "[play=nodeka.com:23]\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>REAL-TIME overhead map displaying TRUE field of vision<\/li>\r\n<li>450+ skills and spells including: mental blast, joufu's arc, north wind<\/li>\r\n<li>120+ classes including: monk, poliir, nojohr, khehusod, ataelos, ruanbaere<\/li>\r\n<li>70+ races, such as: black drake, cloud giant, pixie, ryven, jerof, kedoeji<\/li>\r\n<li>A quest system that'll blow your mind:<\/li>\r\n<li><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\">Story-like quests that have multiple outcomes<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\">A morality system based on YOUR quest DECISIONS<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\">Stored all completed quests - see summaries whenever you want<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\">Tracked open quests and current state - pick up wherever you left\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\">off (have tons of open quests and never forget where you are)<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\">A skill\/spell system using 'preventions' that create not only a fast\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\">paced, but a highly strategic, combat system<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\">Customizable output - including shrinking and expanding combat\u00a0<\/span><span style=\"line-height: 1.3em;\">output and hiding things you don't want to see<\/span><\/li>\r\n<li>Customizable color - battle color, score sheet, who, etc.<\/li>\r\n<li>A million other things we don't have the space to list! Check us out!!<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>"
		}
	},
