	"2e3c9e69-1f9e-4647-8d13-4e88094d2790":  {
		"0":  {
			"value": "[play=burningpost2.co.uk:4321]<br \/><br \/>The Burning Post II is a roleplaying-enforced MUD set on a small island that has been ravaged by mages, demons, and invading forces. The roleplay primarily revolves around mages and the priests\/knights that hunt them. The code has been upgraded substantially in the past year, and the staff looks forward to welcoming new players interested in seeing exactly what we have to offer. Most character concepts don't require immortal approval, so once you get your character looking as you'd like and set the appropriate skills, you can jump right in the game!<br \/><br \/> In addition to the Orderites and Reeves, guilds include the merchants, the thieves (Brotherhood), the Chimerists (a scholarly organization), and the reeves (secular law enforcement).<br \/><br \/>We hope to see you in New Yarsith!"
		}
	},
