			"value": "[play=wayfar1444.com:7777]<br \/><br \/>Wayfar 1444 is a text based online multiplayer game. You are a colonist, sent to the surface of an alien world with a few basic supplies. Join up with other colonists, or plot against them, while surviving and building a self sufficient colony.<br \/><br \/>Wayfar features a procedurally generated galaxy, a distinctive dice pool combat system, hacking, robots, aircraft, vehicles, starships, buildings, detailed crafting, easy to understand english command syntax, and a friendly admin staff."
		}
